invalid type: string "SECTION 511\nOffense: Attempting to commit offences punishable with imprisonment for life, or imprisonment, and in such attempt doing any act towards the commission of the offence\nPunishment: Imprisonment for Life or Imprisonment not exceeding, half of the longest term provided for the Offence, or Fine, or Both\nCognizable: Same As for Offence attempted\npect’4/y’’’’’’’’’’’’